<h2>⚠️ Account Suspension Notice</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Your Matchify.pro account has been suspended.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Suspension Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
    <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}}</p>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{effectiveDate}}</p>
    {{#if endDate}}
    <p><strong>Suspension Ends:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>You cannot register for new tournaments</li>
    <li>Existing registrations remain valid</li>
    <li>You can still view your profile and history</li>
</ul>

{{#if appealUrl}}
<a href="{{appealUrl}}" class="button">Submit Appeal</a>
{{/if}}

<p>If you believe this is a mistake, please contact <a href="mailto:support@matchify.pro">support@matchify.pro</a>.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>Team Matchify</p>
